  "url": "https://www.lankadeepa.lk/latest_news/\u0d86\u0dc4\u0dcf\u0dbb-\u0dc0\u0dbb\u0dca\u0d9c-\u0daf\u0dc4\u0dba\u0d9a\u0dca-\u0dc0\u0dd2\u0dc0\u0dd8\u0dad-\u0d87\u0dab\u0dc0\u0dd4\u0db8\u0dca-\u0d9a\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0db8\u0dba-\u0dba\u0da7\u0dad\u0dda-\u0d86\u0db1\u0dba\u0db1\u0dba\u0da7/1-615379",
  "time_ut": 1656164273,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0d86\u0dc4\u0dcf\u0dbb \u0dc0\u0dbb\u0dca\u0d9c \u0daf\u0dc4\u0dba\u0d9a\u0dca \u0dc0\u0dd2\u0dc0\u0dd8\u0dad \u0d87\u0dab\u0dc0\u0dd4\u0db8\u0dca \u0d9a\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0db8\u0dba \u0dba\u0da7\u0dad\u0dda \u0d86\u0db1\u0dba\u0db1\u0dba\u0da7",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Ten dishes to be imported under the open order system",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Government has taken steps to allow the importation of ten essential commodities under the open order system.",
        "According to government sources, a special circular will be issued on the 1st of this month.",
        "This will enable the importation of 10 essential commodities including rice, sugar dhal milk powder, dried chillies, big onions, sprats, potatoes through the bank without opening a letter of credit and the payment will be made upon agreement between the supplier and the importer. Will be provided.",
        "This system has been in operation before but was banned by the Central Bank on May 8.",
        "Sources say the government will take this decision to prevent a shortage of essential commodities."
      ],
